THE GAME
--------

  'Angoes' is a Workbench game played on an 8 by 8 tile board, the
idea is to align 3 or more of the coloured angles so they are
pointing in the same direction. The catch is that any angle can
only point in 2 directions: either left and right or up and down.

  When 3 or more angles are aligned, they are removed from the
game board and the angles located in the upper spaces will fall
in the emptied spaces.

  Have fun!

